data.name: OracleRCosts_Info2
data.value:
If the part has a resource value already then that value is used
If no value for the part is found, then the Cost Group, Diameter and Length is used to find a match in the averages table - if a match is found that is used.
If no match with the averages is found then the nearest averages are used to form a composite average

data.name: OracleRCosts_Info4
data.value:
If the particular combination of cost group, diameter & length of the override already exists then the override value will replace it
If the particular combination of cost group, diameter & length of the override DOES NOT exist then the override value will be added to the existing list of values and used when calculating the cost.
